node.text:
Life is busy, and preparing a nutritious packed lunch for kids that’s full of what you want them to eat vs what they will actually eat is a bit of a balancing act. I’ve teamed up with @tescofood to give you a whole bunch of tips & recipes to help you lovely lot out. First up I’m giving you the basic principles of a balanced sandwich, so you can mix and match the filling, based on your kids’ needs. Hit the link in my bio for all the recipes and more over on @tescofood 
#TescoandJamie #BackToSchool

Lovely people Together is OUT NOW in the UK !!! This book has been a real labour of love and I’m so excited to see your cook ups !! It’s all about giving you an excuse to get your nearest and dearest together for a good meal, whether you fancy brunch, lunch, a table for two or a full-on feast. And of course, I’ve got plenty of those all-important puds. I’ve set out to create really useful, easy-to-follow recipes that allow you to get organised and get ahead, making it easy to dish up memorable meals for your loved ones. Let me know if you've got your copy yet or gifting it to your favourite food lover in your life! Link to order in my bio. Big love JOX
#JamiesTogether #PublicationDay

Life is busy, and preparing a nutritious packed lunch for kids that’s full of what you want them to eat vs what they will actually eat is a bit of a balancing act. I’ve teamed up with @tescofood to give you a whole bunch of tips & recipes to help you lovely lot out. First up I’m giving you the basic principles of a balanced sandwich, so you can mix and match the filling, based on your kids’ needs. Hit the link in my bio for all the recipes and more over on @tescofood 
#TescoandJamie #BackToSchool
